Brix walks down back to the CR Chambers where Fliq is. When he walks 
in, he gets a huge surprise.

"Ramulus! Long time no see. We were wondering where you were. We'd 
love to talk, but Fliq and I have a mission. We're going to the moon 
to collect parts for the ship. We even sorta named the shuttle after 
in you. In fact, if you're not to busy, you could come with us. We 
could use the help."
